folder: Murray Hulbert Avenu & Water Street, Staten Island, NY
text:
Murray Hulbert Avenue, between Water and Sands Streets, showing the broken pavement and the broken concrete bulkhead on the site of the Foreign Trade Zone. View 1 shows also the south side of pier 13; view 2 the south side of pier 14.

October 19, 1936
Views 1, 2

P. L. Sperr
title: Richmond: Murray Hulbert Avenu - Water Street
